trans-unit.source: Consists of a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects to be used with catalogs of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: A folyamatkészletből <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> katalógusok a használni kívánt objektumok <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> szabályozza.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Ez az osztály nem örökölhető.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is created by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in their implementations of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: A WebPartDescriptionCollection osztály hozta létre a különböző <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>a rendszerbeli szabályozza a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>metódus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: For each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that is contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object is created.
trans-unit.target: Az egyes <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>lévő vezérlő egy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>vezérlő, egy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objektum létrehozása.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: This object maintains basic information about a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, including its ID, its title, its description, and a path to an associated icon.
trans-unit.target: Ez az objektum kapcsolatos alapvető információk tart fenn a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>vezérlő, beleértve az azonosítója, címét, leírását és egy társított ikon elérési útját.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls can use a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to display a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control's information in the catalog, without having to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control itself.
trans-unit.target: A különböző <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>vezérlők használhatja egy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>megjelenítendő objektum egy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>vezérlő a katalógus információi között, anélkül, hogy egy példányának létrehozása a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>szabályozása magát.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is used internally by the Web Parts control set to maintain a collection of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects used in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: A WebPartDescriptionCollection osztály belsőleg a kijelzők vezérlőelem összes karbantartása beállítása a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>katalógusban használt objektumok.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection collection is used only when a page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: A WebPartDescriptionCollection gyűjtemény használata csak akkor, ha egy lap katalógus megjelenítési módban van.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control is being rendered, it loops through the WebPartDescriptionCollection collection, adding the information from each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to the displayed catalog.
trans-unit.target: Ha egy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>vezérlő folyamatban van, akkor végighalad a WebPartDescriptionCollection gyűjtemény hozzáadni az információkat az egyes <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objektum megjelenített katalógus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Egy üres új példányát inicializálja a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> osztály.

trans-unit.source: This overload of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor can be used to create an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Ez túlterhelése a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>konstruktor segítségével hozzon létre egy üres gyűjteményt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control creates an empty <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> object if the content of an imported description file is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Például a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>vezérlő létrehoz egy üres <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection>objektumot, ha egy importált leírás fájl tartalma `null`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> object by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Egy új példányát inicializálja a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> történő az objektum egy <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>gyűjteménye <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objektumok.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection constructor is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method implementations within the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls to create a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects.
trans-unit.target: A WebPartDescriptionCollection konstruktor használják a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>belül a különböző módszer megvalósítások <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>vezérlők egy gyűjteményének létrehozásához <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objektumok.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects that correspond to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: Gyűjteménye <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objektumok, amelyek megfelelnek a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> vezérlők katalógusba.
